"{\"uid\": \"independent.co.uk-news-uk-home-news-imane-khelif-dsd-xy-chromosome-test-paris-2024-olympics-b2634042.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Notifications can be managed in browser preferences.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 52, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in  Swipe for next article  'Is sex something that you can see depending on which hormone, estrogen, or testosterone you preferentially produce?\", \"from\": 54, \"to\": 332, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 279, \"end\": 287, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Estrogen\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.634180938185173e-16, \"text\": \"estrogen\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Estrogen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Estrogen\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"No, it's not.\", \"from\": 333, \"to\": 346, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sex is much more complicated,' expert tellsMaya Oppenheim  Removed from bookmarks  I would like to be emailed about offers, events and updates from The Independent.\", \"from\": 347, \"to\": 511, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy notice  Earlier this year, the often overlooked issue of differences in sex development came to the fore after two women boxers were allowed tocompete in the Olympics after previously failing a gender eligibility test.\", \"from\": 512, \"to\": 746, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Last year, Algeria'sImane Khelifwas disqualified just hours before her gold-medal bout at the women's World Championships in New Delhi after not meeting theInternational Boxing Association's(IBA) eligibility criteria, which blocks athletes with male XY chromosomes competing in women's events.\", \"from\": 748, \"to\": 1041, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 873, \"end\": 882, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Delhi\", \"score\": 0.9999940929607717, \"rank\": 5.907066026392363e-06, \"text\": \"New Delhi\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Delhi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Delhi\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Meanwhile, Taiwan's double-world championLin Yu-tinglost her bronze medal at the same competition after she also failed to meet the criteria.\", \"from\": 1043, \"to\": 1184, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1054, \"end\": 1060, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taiwan\", \"score\": 0.9993019450022738, \"rank\": 0.0006374422382427144, \"text\": \"Taiwan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taiwan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taiwan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On Tuesday, it emerged Khelif is set toturn professional after winning Olympic gold in Paris.\", \"from\": 1186, \"to\": 1279, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1273, \"end\": 1278, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999816726864628, \"rank\": 1.832764951242352e-05, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"TheInternational Olympic Committee(IOC) previously defended its decision to allow the two boxers to compete in theParis 2024 Olympics.\", \"from\": 1281, \"to\": 1415, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1316, \"end\": 1319, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6787250314049124e-20, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It comes after the IBA was stripped of its recognition by the IOC last year over governance and finance issues, with the Olympic body running the boxing competition in Paris itself, and permitting both women to participate.\", \"from\": 1416, \"to\": 1639, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1435, \"end\": 1438, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.9998514111349043, \"rank\": 0.0001485568120338298, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\"}, {\"begin\": 1478, \"end\": 1481, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6787250314049124e-20, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 1584, \"end\": 1589, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999816726864628, \"rank\": 1.832764951242352e-05, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The committee said: \\\"The current aggression against these two athletes is based entirely on this arbitrary decision, which was taken without any proper procedure, especially considering that these athletes had been competing in top-level competition for many years.\", \"from\": 1641, \"to\": 1906, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The IOC is saddened by the abuse that the two athletes are currently receiving.\", \"from\": 1908, \"to\": 1988, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1913, \"end\": 1916, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.6787250314049124e-20, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Every person has the right to practice sport without discrimination.\\\"\", \"from\": 1989, \"to\": 2058, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This raises the question of what differences in sex development are - withThe Independentspeaking to an academic who specialises in this area to find out more.\", \"from\": 2060, \"to\": 2219, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The term \\\"differences in sex development\\\", or DSD, is used to refer to a wide range of different scenarios, with the NHS describing it as a \\\"group of rare conditions involving genes, hormones and reproductive organs, including genitals\\\" which \\\"means a person's sex development is different to most other people's\\\".\", \"from\": 2221, \"to\": 2535, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2267, \"end\": 2270, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Direct_Stream_Digital\", \"score\": 0.8879232359366607, \"rank\": 0.12622348366088512, \"text\": \"DSD\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Direct_Stream_Digital\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Direct_Stream_Digital\"}, {\"begin\": 2338, \"end\": 2341, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Health_Service\", \"score\": 0.9799827524756018, \"rank\": 0.020426068906416964, \"text\": \"NHS\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Health_Service\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Health_Service\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Individuals can either have sex chromosomes generally linked with being female (XX chromosomes) or usually associated with being a man (XY chromosomes), yet have reproductive organs and genitals that may look different.\", \"from\": 2537, \"to\": 2756, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2617, \"end\": 2619, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/XY_sex-determination_system\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.901332747606762e-39, \"text\": \"XX\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/XY_sex-determination_system\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/XY_sex-determination_system\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Enjoy 185+ fights a year on DAZN, the Global Home of Boxing  Never miss a fight from top promoters.\", \"from\": 2758, \"to\": 2857, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2786, \"end\": 2790, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/DAZN\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.1013677741255445e-20, \"text\": \"DAZN\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/DAZN\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/DAZN\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Watch on your devices anywhere, anytime.\", \"from\": 2858, \"to\": 2898, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ADVERTISEMENT.\", \"from\": 2900, \"to\": 2914, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If you sign up to this service we will earn commission.This revenue helps to fund journalism across The Independent.\", \"from\": 2915, \"to\": 3031, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Enjoy 185+ fights a year on DAZN, the Global Home of Boxing  Never miss a fight from top promoters.\", \"from\": 3033, \"to\": 3132, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3061, \"end\": 3065, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/DAZN\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.1013677741255445e-20, \"text\": \"DAZN\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/DAZN\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/DAZN\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Watch on your devices anywhere, anytime.\", \"from\": 3133, \"to\": 3173, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"ADVERTISEMENT.\", \"from\": 3175, \"to\": 3189, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If you sign up to this service we will earn commission.This revenue helps to fund journalism across The Independent.\", \"from\": 3190, \"to\": 3306, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The NHS states that \\\"a person may have a womb and may also have testicles inside their body.\", \"from\": 3308, \"to\": 3400, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3312, \"end\": 3315, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Health_Service\", \"score\": 0.9799827524756018, \"rank\": 0.020426068906416964, \"text\": \"NHS\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Health_Service\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Health_Service\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sometimes the testicles might not work properly\\\".\", \"from\": 3401, \"to\": 3450, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It adds: \\\"Some people with a very rare type of DSD have both ovarian and testicular tissue (sometimes one ovary and one testis).\", \"from\": 3452, \"to\": 3580, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3499, \"end\": 3502, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Direct_Stream_Digital\", \"score\": 0.8879232359366607, \"rank\": 0.12622348366088512, \"text\": \"DSD\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Direct_Stream_Digital\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Direct_Stream_Digital\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Their genitals may appear female or male or could look different from either.\\\"\", \"from\": 3581, \"to\": 3659, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A person may have a womb and may also have testicles inside their body.\", \"from\": 3661, \"to\": 3732, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sometimes the testicles might not work properly  Claus H\\u00f8jbjerg Gravholt, a professor of genetic endocrinology, said it is impossible to state everyone with a Y chromosome is a male and everyone with an X chromosome is a female.\", \"from\": 3733, \"to\": 3961, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3788, \"end\": 3796, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/H\\u00f8jbjerg\", \"score\": 0.9764823238924786, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"H\\u00f8jbjerg\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/H\\u00f8jbjerg\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/H\\u00f8jbjerg\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Professor H\\u00f8jbjerg Gravholt, who is based at Aarhus University in Denmark and works with patients who have differences in sex development, added: \\\"If I showed you pictures of my patients without any clothes on, you would say, well, these are females that I am looking at.\", \"from\": 3963, \"to\": 4234, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3973, \"end\": 3981, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/H\\u00f8jbjerg\", \"score\": 0.9764823238924786, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"H\\u00f8jbjerg\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/H\\u00f8jbjerg\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/H\\u00f8jbjerg\"}, {\"begin\": 4008, \"end\": 4025, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aarhus_University\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.588226738020579e-28, \"text\": \"Aarhus University\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aarhus_University\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aarhus_University\"}, {\"begin\": 4029, \"end\": 4036, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Denmark\", \"score\": 0.999999869417033, \"rank\": 1.298751752253634e-07, \"text\": \"Denmark\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Denmark\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Denmark\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But, in fact, they actually have a Y chromosome.\", \"from\": 4236, \"to\": 4285, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And so it's really coming back to, what is sex?\", \"from\": 4286, \"to\": 4333, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Is sex something you can see out of the chromosomes?\", \"from\": 4334, \"to\": 4386, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"No, it's not.\", \"from\": 4387, \"to\": 4400, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Is sex something that you can see\\u00a0depending on which hormone, estrogen, or testosterone you preferentially produce?\", \"from\": 4401, \"to\": 4516, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4463, \"end\": 4471, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Estrogen\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.634180938185173e-16, \"text\": \"estrogen\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Estrogen\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Estrogen\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"No, it's not.\", \"from\": 4517, \"to\": 4530, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sex is much more complicated.\\\"\", \"from\": 4531, \"to\": 4561, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"People generally find out they have a difference in sex development around when they are born or once they become a teenager.\", \"from\": 4563, \"to\": 4688, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But Professor H\\u00f8jbjerg Gravholt explained the last patient he had diagnosed was a woman in her early thirties who had sought help as she could not get pregnant.\", \"from\": 4690, \"to\": 4850, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4704, \"end\": 4712, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/H\\u00f8jbjerg\", \"score\": 0.9764823238924786, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"H\\u00f8jbjerg\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/H\\u00f8jbjerg\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/H\\u00f8jbjerg\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"She had a normal vagina, a normal external female appearance, but did not have a uterus, and she also produced a lot of testosterone from her two testes, which were placed at the same place as the ovaries,\\\" he added.\", \"from\": 4852, \"to\": 5069, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Her experience demonstrates how complicated differences in sex development are, he said, explaining the patient was \\\"devastated\\\" when he told her that she could not get pregnant due to not having a uterus.\", \"from\": 5071, \"to\": 5276, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Professor H\\u00f8jbjerg Gravholt explains around half of the patients he sees do not have a uterus so they can not carry a child through a pregnancy - while the other half have a uterus, but do not produce eggs.\", \"from\": 5278, \"to\": 5484, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5288, \"end\": 5296, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/H\\u00f8jbjerg\", \"score\": 0.9764823238924786, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"H\\u00f8jbjerg\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/H\\u00f8jbjerg\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/H\\u00f8jbjerg\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"These women would not have periods unless they are given sex hormones, he explained, adding that he has never encountered or heard of a woman with an XY chromosome who can have children.\", \"from\": 5486, \"to\": 5672, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5636, \"end\": 5638, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/XY_sex-determination_system\", \"score\": 0.9999999999545253, \"rank\": 4.565263840387612e-11, \"text\": \"XY\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/XY_sex-determination_system\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/XY_sex-determination_system\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Join thought-provoking conversations, follow other Independent readers and see their replies  Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in\", \"from\": 5674, \"to\": 5904, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5725, \"end\": 5736, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.1636605588721555e-15, \"text\": \"Independent\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\"}]}]}"